I"É<h3 id="search">Search</h3>

<p>At the top, next to menu bar, search bar is displayed. This will be a section for users to search barcode by either typing or scanning the barcode.</p>

<p>A record will be diplayed of the child. The barcode sticker is place on page four(4) of the childs booklet.</p>

<p>If record is not found, kindly use the advance search as explained in advance search section.</p>

